Usage: reportCritInstance [-help] -outfile <string> [-targetSlack <float>]
                          [-view <string>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
-outfile <string>     # <outfile> (string, required)
-targetSlack <float>  # <targetSlack> (float, optional)
-view <string>        # <viewName> (string, optional)